tip.text: Bread! And the pancakes with bacon! And the affogato!
My friends love the waffles here, coming all the way from AMK for it. And affogato with pistachio ice cream may sound like a strange combo but it works!

contact.facebookName: The Milky Way Homemade Ice Cream and Coffee

tip.text: The cakes here are pretty amazing, and the coffees pretty good too. So nice to have a place like this right near where I work when I need a coffee and cake fix.

venue.name: Sanpoutei Ramen 三宝亭らーめん
Menya Musashi Kodou 麺屋武蔵

tip.text: Nice and bright atmosphere in a green environment. Take a table outside if it's not too hot. Really nice. The citron tart is the handsomest I've ever seen and tastes pretty good too.

formattedAddress: #01-12, The Metropolis (9 North Buona Vista Dr.)

tip.text: Coffee's pretty good. Cute company too. They also have an array of cakes, including different flavored Thai crepe cakes. A nice, quiet tucked away in a corner, perfect for whiling away an hour or two.
Balsamic tomatoes and bacon with scrambled eggs. And of course, the coffee. Haven't tried the cakes yet but they look so good that I'm dying to.
